{
  "stem": "21919.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew the prayers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew how to cross myself, but I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was always sitting close to the confession booth, and observing people, and listening in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when I went to confession, I thought that I-- I knew exactly what to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I crossed myself, and I said, that-- I-- Father, I wanted to confess.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I thought I did everything just perfect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then when you come after the confession, you kneel in front of-- of-- of the priest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's like a-- like a stage, and you kneel in front of that stage, which were about a dozen people or more.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You close your eyes, you open your mouth, and you get--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A wafer, so I did that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the priest went right by me and didn't give me the wafer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my heart almost stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know if he just missed me by accident or he knew that I was Jewish and he didn't give it to me there and he wasn't fooled by anything that I said.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was waiting for him to go and tell the people that I worked for what my problem is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that didn't happen for a day, and it didn't happen for a while.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I kept thinking that it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I start asking for other people, if they knew who needed-- who need another-- a-- somebody to work for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And I found a different place, a smaller family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was closer to-- to town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a few-- a few miles away from where I worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't know how I figured I was safe there, but it was safer than going back to church.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
